name: Colorful Hills and White Tree original acrylic painting on wood
description:
This sweet little painting is acrylic paint on recycled and stained three quarter inch plywood. I love it! So simple, yet so beautiful in person.

Painting Dimensions: 4.5 x 5.25 x .75 inches

Ready to hang on back with a D ring.

*The price of the painting is half of what it would fetch in a gallery.

Thanks for looking!
Courtney Oquist

name: Bonjour art postcard
description:
Remember postcards? I do! Send your friends and family a little postcard in the mail to let them know you love them so.

About this postcard:

Measures 4 x 6 inches with rounded corners, printed professionally on heavy cardstock with satin finish. The reverse side is blank, save my name and website info on bottom.

Artwork by Courtney Oquist.

Please see my website for more info!
www.courtneyoquist.com

name: Lovely Landscape art print
description:
This is a print of one of my original ink and watercolor works on paper that was scanned and also digitally colored a little.

-------About the Print-------
Printed on matte Epson art paper using UltraChrome archival pigment fine art inks.

Total print size: 8.5 x 11 inches. (there is an approx. 1 inch white border.)

Signed and dated by artist in pencil in lower right corner of image. Prints arrive sealed in cello sleeves and protected in a cardboard mailer.

For more info, please visit my websites:
www.courtneyoquist.com
www.artistscookbook.com

Thank you! :)
Courtney Oquist

name: On the Inside fine art print 8 x 8 inches
description:
This is a digital print of one of my original waterless lithographic prints. I used the rib cage as a starting point to draw in what I thought a woman would look like over it. I think it's really neat that we all have this amazing complete skeletal frame beneath our skin that we never actually see.

-------About the Print-------
Printed on matte Epson paper using archival fine art inks.

Total print size: 8 x 8 inches. (the image measures around 6 x 6 inches and is centered with white border.)

Signed and dated by artist in pencil in lower right corner of image. Prints arrive sealed in cello sleeves and protected in a cardboard mailer.

For more info, please visit my websites:
www.courtneyoquist.com
www.artistscookbook.com

Thank you! :)
Courtney Oquist

name: rrrraoul postcard
